OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FFine and chilly to start with
OL,6,Fsome sunshine, however cloud soon
OL,7,Fthickening from the west to bring a
OL,8,Flittle rain in places as winds pick
OL,9,Fup. Rather cloudy, with winds
OL,10,Fstrengthening further during the
OL,11,Fafternoon. Mild in shelter.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FBecoming very windy, with
OL,14,Finland gales, perhaps severe for a
OL,15,Ftime, coupled with heavy rain and
OL,16,Fblustery showers. Becoming drier and
OL,17,Fclearer through the early hours, with
OL,18,Fwinds easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
