OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FA colder-feeling day, bright
OL,6,Fand breezy at first with limited sunny
OL,7,Fintervals, but giving way to cloud and
OL,8,Frain or showers. Becoming drier and
OL,9,Fbrighter again later, with winds
OL,10,Feasing.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMainly
OL,13,Ffine through this period, with some
OL,14,Fwarm days and sunny periods after
OL,15,Fchilly starts. Perhaps becoming more
OL,16,Funsettled from the west midweek.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
